title: Morning Joe 2/26/21
description: A ruling in the Senate on Thursday dealt a blow to Democrats' effort to raise the federal minimum wage to $15 in the Covid-19 relief package. Is there room to negotiate on raising the minimum wage? The Morning Joe panel discusses.
author: news.podcasts@nbcuni.com (NBC News)
